      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   exe-cph-com-000      thru exe-cph-com-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su valori letti                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-inp-com-txt        =    spaces
